    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have got to see this beauty! I\u2019ve taken such good care of this car, and honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014not a scratch or a dent anywhere! I'm so excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. It\u2019s super reliable and ready for its next adventure today. Let's get you in for a test drive!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
