    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom-quality condition, this vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream. The exterior paint retains its factory-fresh depth and luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing or bolster wear, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the high-fidelity sound system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been meticulously maintained exclusively at authorized service centers, with a complete binder of service records included to verify its history. The engine bay is immaculate, and the transmission shifts with silk-like precision. It sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires with virtually no wear. This is a meticulously preserved specimen intended for the most discerning buyer. Pre-purchase inspections at a specialist of your choice are welcomed and encouraged.",
      "price": 46500.0,
