    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute gem of a car, and let me tell you, it is in incredible shape! It\u2019s been so well-loved that it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is spotless. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
