    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a pristine example of Bavarian engineering. The S54 inline-six remains internally stock with a recently serviced double-VANOS system ensuring optimal cam phasing. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, short-throw engagement, delivering power to the rear wheels via a perfectly functioning M-Variable differential lock. Subframe reinforcement has been completed as a preventative measure, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral G-loads. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping, and the throttle response from the individual throttle bodies is instantaneous. Truly a collector-grade chassis with zero mechanical compromises.",
